::Stratus::

Stratus shakes himself, drops of ocean water falling all around him. 
He looks around. Stratus had surfaced several seconds ago on the 
shore of North America, as close to the Decepticon base as he could 
get. The Decepticons were the faction that he had been created to 
join.

Taking off at a jog, Stratus looks around him, memorizing the terrain.
